BEGIN_PGML We can also compute the total number of dots by summing each "hook" region, from smallest to largest:
[_]{1}{3} \+ [_]{3}{3} \+ [_]{5}{3} \+ [_]{7}{3} \+ [_]{9}{3} \+ [_]{11}{4}.
END_PGML
